See important comments concerning validity of position given in sectionNavigation Output Filters.This message outputs the Geodetic position in the currently selected ellipsoid. The default isthe WGS84 Ellipsoid, but can be changed with the message CFG-DAT.

column7: GPS time of week of the navigation epoch.See the description of iTOW for details.
